title: The Cigar of the Year Edition
itunes:title: The Cigar of the Year Edition
description: Since 1992 David Garofalo has been naming The Cigar of the Year, and for the 24th time, we will do so today; the day before Super Bowl Sunday in our time honored tradtion...We well smoke the 2014 COTY BG Meyer one last time and then light up the 2015 Cigar of the Year...Who will it be? Tune in and find out!﻿
